\item Fixed a bug illustrated by the following code, which gave
      an error saying that \code{p[1,1]} has the wrong number of subscripts:
\preformatted{   p <- pairlist(1,2,3,4); dim(p) <- c(2,2); p[1,1] <- 9
}
